it.escape.core.client.controller.gui

Interface UpdaterSwingToViewInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SmartSwingView

    public interface UpdaterSwingToViewInterface
    This interface contains the methods in the Swing View that can be invoked directly by the UpdaterSwing. UpdaterSwing uses this class to modify the Swing View.

    michele
